articles.title: Millions of Americans caught up in Chinese hacking plot - US - BBC.com
articles.description: Seven Chinese men have been charged over a "sinister" hacking plot, the justice department says.

articles.title: US Moon Lander 'Permanently' Asleep After Historic Landing - Newsmax
articles.description: An uncrewed American lander that became the first private spaceship on the moon has met its ultimate end after failing to "wake up," the company that built it said.
